{"about_the_game":"Dragon Courier is an open-world RPG, influenced by classic JRPG and CRPG genres.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332040/extras/DC_List_1.gif?t=1723503759\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2>A strong wind blows across the world and refuses to stop. Fearing a bad omen, people grow suspicious of one another as a dark age descends. Increasing corruption and greed lures out evil creatures from the mountain depths, looking to pilfer from vulnerable travelers. As a courier for the Dragon Dispatch, you provide secure delivery of goods. Start with simple tasks and build towards bigger jobs, taking you across the world into the middle of a larger story.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Large Open-World Exploration <br></li><li>Strategic Turn-Based Combat<br></li><li>Diverse Quests<br></li><li>Rich Storyline<br></li><li>Dungeon Crawling<br></li><li>Cloud Saving<br></li><li>Controller Support<br></li><li>Fishing!</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332040/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1723503759","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332040/page.bg.jpg?t=1723503759","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332040/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1723503759","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332040/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1723503759","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Dragon Courier is an open-world RPG, influenced by classic JRPG and CRPG genres.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332040/extras/DC_List_1.gif?t=1723503759\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2>A strong wind blows across the world and refuses to stop. Fearing a bad o